tps://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4708.jpg 1024w, https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4708-300x225.jpg 300w, https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4708-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-492\" src=\"https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4721-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4721.jpg 1024w, https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4721-300x225.jpg 300w, https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4721-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-493\" src=\"https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4725-e1518729901521-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" srcset=\"https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4725-e1518729901521.jpg 768w, https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4725-e1518729901521-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-494\" src=\"https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4732-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4732.jpg 1024w, https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4732-300x225.jpg 300w, https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4732-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-495\" src=\"https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4728-e1518729970432-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" srcset=\"https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4728-e1518729970432.jpg 768w, https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4728-e1518729970432-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-496\" src=\"https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4731-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4731.jpg 1024w, https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4731-300x225.jpg 300w, https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4731-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-497\" src=\"https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4706-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4706.jpg 1024w, https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4706-300x225.jpg 300w, https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4706-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-498\" src=\"https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4993-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4993.jpg 1024w, https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4993-300x225.jpg 300w, https://plant-collage.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/IMG_4993-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Ok I lied.  I&#8217;ll come back and label all of these once I get positive IDs for the plants.</p>\n<p>I hope you enjoyed these pics.  Back to the wet, gray Northwest for a while now!</p>\n","date":"February 15, 2018","categories":[{"name":"California","slug":"california"},{"name":"In Nature","slug":"in-nature"},{"name":"Succulents","slug":"succulents"}],"tags":null,"author":{"name":"susan","slug":"susan"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"6bf1388e-a10f-514f-a640-7aad52cc40ae"}}}